# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebaq1.rpy:10
translate spanish rebaq1_5a3ee789:

    # rb "Do you know anything about car repair?"
    rb "¿Sabes algo de reparación de coches?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebaq1.rpy:11
translate spanish rebaq1_6ba52186:

    # pc "A little. I used to work on my dad's car with him sometimes."
    pc "Un poco. A veces solía trabajar en el coche de mi padre con él."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebaq1.rpy:13
translate spanish rebaq1_e8620003:

    # rb "Your daddy's not around anymore either?"
    rb "¿Tu padre tampoco está ya por aquí?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebaq1.rpy:14
translate spanish rebaq1_e85513db:

    # pc "He's not dead. At least I hope he's not. He's just missing. I've been trying to find him."
    pc "No está muerto. Al menos espero que no lo esté. Solo está desaparecido. He estado intentando encontrarlo."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebaq1.rpy:15
translate spanish rebaq1_544d26f8:

    # rb "Oh, I'm sorry. I didn't know."
    rb "Oh, lo siento. No lo sabía."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebaq1.rpy:16
translate spanish rebaq1_7b4b4f22:

    # pc "It's okay. I'm worried about it, but I try not to let it consume my whole life, you know?"
    pc "No pasa nada. Me preocupa, pero intento que no me consuma la vida, ¿sabes?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebaq1.rpy:18
translate spanish rebaq1_39ca944f:

    # rb "Yeah, that makes sense."
    rb "Sí, tiene sentido."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebaq1.rpy:19
translate spanish rebaq1_0a08a1cd:

    # pc "Anyway... cars. How did you learn about them?"
    pc "Bueno... los coches. ¿Cómo aprendiste sobre ellos?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebaq1.rpy:21
translate spanish rebaq1_fc262be9:

    # rb "Mostly from YouTube."
    rb "Sobre todo en YouTube."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebaq1.rpy:23
translate spanish rebaq1_d31ea6b7:

    # rb "My daddy used to work on the cars some, but he always had a six-pack next to him while he did it."
    rb "Mi padre solía arreglar un poco los coches, pero siempre tenía un pack de seis cervezas a su lado mientras lo hacía."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebaq1.rpy:24
translate spanish rebaq1_2a3f7acd:

    # rb "Mama didn't like me to be around him when he was drinking. So I didn't learn much about cars from him."
    rb "A mi madre no le gustaba que estuviera con él cuando bebía. Así que no aprendí mucho sobre coches de él."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebaq1.rpy:26
translate spanish rebaq1_c318459c:

    # rb "But the guys up at the garage have taught me a lot."
    rb "Pero los chicos del taller me han enseñado un montón."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebaq1.rpy:27
translate spanish rebaq1_dd096c0a:

    # rb "They like having me around, teaching me stuff. It's like having five daddies."
    rb "Les gusta tenerme cerca, enseñarme cosas. Es como tener cinco papás."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebaq1.rpy:28
translate spanish rebaq1_194e2c3d:

    # pc "Does it ever get weird? You hanging around with five older guys?"
    pc "¿Alguna vez resulta raro? ¿Andar con cinco tíos mayores?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebaq1.rpy:30
translate spanish rebaq1_1b066b64:

    # rb "Weird? Nah."
    rb "¿Raro? No."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebaq1.rpy:31
translate spanish rebaq1_91cb5233:

    # rb "They can get a little raunchy at times, but they treat me right."
    rb "A veces pueden ponerse un poco obscenos, pero me tratan bien."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebaq1.rpy:32
translate spanish rebaq1_8f15abb5:

    # rb "They wouldn't mess with me."
    rb "No se meterían conmigo."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebaq1.rpy:34
translate spanish rebaq1_97d96548:

    # rb "They've seen how I can bust a nut, you know?"
    rb "Han visto cómo puedo romper una tuerca, ¿sabes?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebaq1.rpy:35
translate spanish rebaq1_d191877a:

    # pc "Um... what?"
    pc "Eh... ¿qué?"

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebaq1.rpy:37
translate spanish rebaq1_438fdd4d:

    # rb "Bust a nut."
    rb "Romper una tuerca."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebaq1.rpy:38
translate spanish rebaq1_7c43468b:

    # rb "You know... when a nut is so tight or rusty or whatever, so you gotta pull out the breaker bar and bust it."
    rb "Ya sabes... cuando una tuerca está muy apretada o oxidada o lo que sea, y tienes que sacar la barra de palanca y romperla."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebaq1.rpy:39
translate spanish rebaq1_7d6bde73:

    # pc "Oh, I got ya."
    pc "Ah, ya te pillo."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebaq1.rpy:41
translate spanish rebaq1_247a7049:

    # rb "Yeah, I'm always busting nuts at the garage."
    rb "Sí, siempre estoy rompiendo tuercas en el taller."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebaq1.rpy:42
translate spanish rebaq1_526b02a4:

    # rb "I'm a lot stronger than I look."
    rb "Soy mucho más fuerte de lo que parezco."

# game/Scenes/Reba/RebaConversations/rebaq1.rpy:43
translate spanish rebaq1_72ecb4f8:

    # pc "I believe you."
    pc "Te creo."

